data.title: Wuman
data.text: Well we wanted to spend time together n we find the right plc .the food the people that was there was good service drinks

data.title: A real trip to Oaxaca without crossing the border!!! Amazing Food
data.text: This place is the must authentic Oaxacan Food I have ever tried, its just amazing food and friendly service!!

data.title: Delicious moles
data.text: Food from southern Mexico. Many different flavor combinations. I will definitely have to try this again.

data.title: Lo Mejor en comida oaxaqueña
data.text: Me encanta benir por sus moles super ricos sus tlayudas con mole las adore su platillo de carnes mixta también es riquísimo mucha tradición oaxaqueña en un solo lugar tortillas echas a mano pero no cualquier tortilla son tortillotas sus precios barian para mi  accesibles su personal siempre amable y atento

owner_response.author: Greg L, Owner at Real De Oaxaca, responded to this review
owner_response.text:
Being the mole fan you are, this review means quite a bit to us! I only wish I'd have seen it sooner (we're a little new to TripAdvisor). Thank you for the kind words, and I hope we'll get the chance to have you back for a meal soon. 

Thanks, 
Greg, Owner
